1
00:00:08,600 --> 00:00:10,961
ظآزLove's little quiz
takes seven parts sweetظآز

2
00:00:10,962 --> 00:00:13,559
ظآزAnd three parts bitter,
till you and I meetظآز

3
00:00:13,560 --> 00:00:17,159
ظآزI pretend I'm not there,
but secretly stayظآز

4
00:00:17,160 --> 00:00:26,399
ظآزWaiting for youظآز

5
00:00:26,400 --> 00:00:31,400
ظآزWe've got so many
romantic dreams to unfoldظآز

6
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:36,224
ظآزFinally hearing
the I love you I long to holdظآز

7
00:00:36,225 --> 00:00:39,839
ظآزFalling fast
into the swirl of your eyesظآز

8
00:00:39,840 --> 00:00:42,399
ظآزIt's just too tempting, so temptingظآز

9
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:45,499
ظآزNever could I have guessedظآز

10
00:00:45,500 --> 00:00:46,499
ظآزMy heart's rhythmظآز

11
00:00:46,500 --> 00:00:49,632
ظآزHow beautiful it is, meeting youظآز

12
00:01:02,975 --> 00:01:05,961
=Late to Love=
(Adapted from "My Husband Is A Billionaire!")

13
00:01:05,962 --> 00:01:08,720
=Episode 9=

14
00:01:10,300 --> 00:01:12,260
Our dear in-laws have arrived.

15
00:01:12,900 --> 00:01:14,459
Forgive me
for not welcoming you properly.

16
00:01:14,460 --> 00:01:15,978
This must be our in-law,

17
00:01:15,979 --> 00:01:17,179
Old Mr. Huo himself!

18
00:01:17,499 --> 00:01:18,819
Really now, dear in-law,

19
00:01:18,820 --> 00:01:20,058
for such an important visit,

20
00:01:20,059 --> 00:01:21,778
you should've told us ahead of time.

21
00:01:21,779 --> 00:01:23,459
Thankfully Mr. Zichen

22
00:01:23,460 --> 00:01:25,019
was thoughtful enough to arrange it.

23
00:01:26,740 --> 00:01:29,140
So it was Zichen's doing all along.

24
00:01:29,180 --> 00:01:32,218
Uncle, it was my own decision.
I wasn't sure whether it was appropriate.

25
00:01:32,219 --> 00:01:33,258
Of course it is.

26
00:01:33,259 --> 00:01:34,579
Very appropriate.

27
00:01:35,540 --> 00:01:37,258
Nange, entertain the guests for now.

28
00:01:37,259 --> 00:01:39,379
I'll head to the kitchen
and make arrangements.

29
00:01:39,380 --> 00:01:41,459
We'll chat more later, in-law.

30
00:01:41,460 --> 00:01:43,579
Sorry for the disturbance, in-law.

31
00:01:43,699 --> 00:01:44,939
Uncle, I'll help you.

32
00:01:44,940 --> 00:01:45,900
Let's go.

33
00:01:46,740 --> 00:01:47,939
Xu Nange,

34
00:01:51,020 --> 00:01:52,579
you'd better give me some face here.

35
00:01:52,580 --> 00:01:54,579
Because if you embarrass me,

36
00:01:54,580 --> 00:01:56,659
you'll only make things unpleasant
for yourself.

37
00:01:56,859 --> 00:01:58,579
After all, this is still the Huo family.

38
00:02:05,660 --> 00:02:08,179
Dear in-law, your presence
truly honors this humble home.

39
00:02:08,180 --> 00:02:10,058
These dishes

40
00:02:10,059 --> 00:02:12,338
were specially prepared
for you by the Huo family.

41
00:02:12,339 --> 00:02:14,378
I just hope they suit your taste.

42
00:02:14,379 --> 00:02:15,218
Please.

43
00:02:15,219 --> 00:02:16,459
Mr. Huo,

44
00:02:16,460 --> 00:02:18,180
you're far too kind.

45
00:02:20,339 --> 00:02:21,419
Auntie,

46
00:02:21,819 --> 00:02:23,620
please try this.

47
00:02:23,700 --> 00:02:24,778
As the head of the family,

48
00:02:24,779 --> 00:02:25,960
you work so hard every day.

49
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:27,200
You should nourish yourself more.

50
00:02:28,740 --> 00:02:30,659
Xu Yin, come.

51
00:02:31,180 --> 00:02:32,300
You should try some too.

52
00:02:32,980 --> 00:02:34,460
Thank you, Zichen.

53
00:02:37,580 --> 00:02:40,460
Zichen is such a thoughtful child.

54
00:02:42,180 --> 00:02:43,299
To be honest,

55
00:02:43,300 --> 00:02:46,338
Nange's had a hard life.
Her biological mother passed away early.

56
00:02:46,339 --> 00:02:48,179
When her father left her in my care,

57
00:02:48,180 --> 00:02:49,979
she was only this tall.

58
00:02:50,260 --> 00:02:51,618
Over the years,

59
00:02:51,619 --> 00:02:53,179
I truly devoted myself to raising her.

60
00:02:53,180 --> 00:02:55,579
I was both mother and father to her.

61
00:02:55,580 --> 00:02:58,378
If other children had something,
then Nange had to have it too.

62
00:02:58,379 --> 00:02:59,899
And if other children didn't have it,

63
00:02:59,900 --> 00:03:02,740
I'd still do everything I could
to get it for her.

64
00:03:03,659 --> 00:03:05,378
Nange, do you still remember

65
00:03:05,379 --> 00:03:07,979
that princess dress you wanted
back in elementary school?

66
00:03:07,980 --> 00:03:09,618
I had to go to three malls

67
00:03:09,619 --> 00:03:10,979
before finally finding it for you.

68
00:03:10,980 --> 00:03:12,859
You've probably forgotten by now,
haven't you?

69
00:03:12,860 --> 00:03:15,099
You still want a new dress?

70
00:03:15,339 --> 00:03:17,259
From now on, just wear

71
00:03:17,260 --> 00:03:19,020
whatever your sister's done with.

72
00:03:19,779 --> 00:03:22,618
Mom, you're way too good to Nange.

73
00:03:22,619 --> 00:03:25,338
I remember when she was living
on campus in high school,

74
00:03:25,339 --> 00:03:27,019
Mom would make soup every weekend

75
00:03:27,020 --> 00:03:28,699
and have me deliver it to her.

76
00:03:29,580 --> 00:03:30,859
That's nothing.

77
00:03:30,860 --> 00:03:32,179
As long as our Nange is doing well,

78
00:03:32,180 --> 00:03:34,139
everything I do is worth it.

79
00:03:34,140 --> 00:03:35,340
Right?

80
00:03:35,340 --> 00:03:36,618
Stop kidding yourself, Xu Nange.

81
00:03:36,619 --> 00:03:38,340
You think someone like you
deserves friends?

82
00:03:38,460 --> 00:03:39,538
From now on,

83
00:03:39,539 --> 00:03:41,419
stop embarrassing me at school, okay?

84
00:03:41,420 --> 00:03:42,538
I already transferred

85
00:03:42,539 --> 00:03:44,179
your allowance to Yin.

86
00:03:44,180 --> 00:03:46,658
Whatever she has left over,
that's what you get to spend.

87
00:03:46,659 --> 00:03:48,139
You won't starve.

88
00:03:48,180 --> 00:03:50,378
And from now on,
stay out of sight around the house.

89
00:03:50,379 --> 00:03:51,739
Seeing you annoys me.

90
00:03:51,740 --> 00:03:52,900
You're bad luck.

91
00:03:59,379 --> 00:04:02,099
This in-law really hasn't had it easy.

92
00:04:02,379 --> 00:04:03,419
Nange,

93
00:04:03,420 --> 00:04:05,060
- from now on you should...
- I understand.

94
00:04:05,659 --> 00:04:06,780
Good.

95
00:04:10,020 --> 00:04:13,099
(I already figured the Xu family
dynamics out back in college.)

96
00:04:13,420 --> 00:04:15,659
(I just didn't expect
they'd become useful now.)

97
00:04:17,179 --> 00:04:18,659
(Nange,)

98
00:04:19,219 --> 00:04:21,220
(how much longer
are you going to endure this?)

99
00:04:21,620 --> 00:04:23,619
(And does Beiyan know any of it?)

100
00:04:23,700 --> 00:04:25,140
(Interesting.)

101
00:04:26,460 --> 00:04:27,418
It's just a pity.

102
00:04:27,419 --> 00:04:30,499
The Xu family is worlds apart
from the Huo family.

103
00:04:30,500 --> 00:04:32,059
Now that's not true at all.

104
00:04:32,060 --> 00:04:33,059
From now on,

105
00:04:33,060 --> 00:04:34,259
we're all one family.

106
00:04:34,260 --> 00:04:35,899
If you ever
have difficulties or requests,

107
00:04:35,900 --> 00:04:37,220
just say the word.

108
00:04:38,620 --> 00:04:39,579
Auntie,

109
00:04:39,580 --> 00:04:41,979
we should spend more time together
from now on.

110
00:04:44,380 --> 00:04:45,418
Zichen's right.

111
00:04:45,419 --> 00:04:47,460
We should pay each other more visits.

112
00:04:48,620 --> 00:04:49,619
Absolutely.

113
00:04:49,620 --> 00:04:51,859
We'll keep in touch often.

114
00:04:57,739 --> 00:04:58,699
(Hurry up.)

115
00:04:58,700 --> 00:05:01,418
(I'm waiting for you to lose control,
Xu Nange.)

116
00:05:01,419 --> 00:05:04,059
Judging by the time,
it should be here soon.

117
00:05:09,380 --> 00:05:10,418
Did you prepare some kind

118
00:05:10,419 --> 00:05:12,340
of surprise for everyone?

119
00:05:12,460 --> 00:05:14,699
Everyone, apologies.

120
00:05:14,700 --> 00:05:17,499
This surprise was prepared
for Nange alone.

121
00:05:28,700 --> 00:05:29,819
Mr. Huo.

122
00:05:29,820 --> 00:05:30,940
Madam.

123
00:05:31,580 --> 00:05:32,858
These are the gifts

124
00:05:32,859 --> 00:05:34,659
Mr. Huo personally prepared for you.

125
00:05:39,659 --> 00:05:42,418
First, the premier collector's piece
from Paris Haute Couture Week.

126
00:05:42,419 --> 00:05:43,419
Second,

127
00:05:43,460 --> 00:05:46,419
a limited-edition set handcrafted
by Italy's national master artisan.

128
00:05:46,659 --> 00:05:47,699
Third,

129
00:05:47,700 --> 00:05:50,539
the final archived treasures
from Paris's last pearl atelier.

130
00:05:52,659 --> 00:05:53,780
And here

131
00:05:55,099 --> 00:05:56,139
this is the Corridor of Time

132
00:05:56,140 --> 00:05:57,859
personally opened for you by Mr. Huo.

133
00:05:57,979 --> 00:05:59,379
Every piece of jewelry inside

134
00:05:59,380 --> 00:06:01,340
holds its own legendary story.

135
00:06:02,460 --> 00:06:03,499
And now,

136
00:06:03,500 --> 00:06:06,139
they're all waiting
to meet you once again.

137
00:06:06,140 --> 00:06:07,218
Oh,

138
00:06:07,219 --> 00:06:08,978
and Mr. Huo specifically instructed us.

139
00:06:08,979 --> 00:06:11,338
There was no need
to choose the most expensive gifts.

140
00:06:11,339 --> 00:06:13,298
What mattered was that each piece

141
00:06:13,299 --> 00:06:14,699
could gain a brand-new life

142
00:06:14,700 --> 00:06:16,700
when worn by you.

143
00:06:20,739 --> 00:06:22,140
(Beiyan.)

144
00:06:23,260 --> 00:06:24,939
(It's only a paper agreement.)

145
00:06:24,940 --> 00:06:27,459
(Do you really have to play her knight
in shining armor too?)

146
00:06:27,460 --> 00:06:29,379
(Can you stop using this fake-love act)

147
00:06:29,380 --> 00:06:30,859
(to disgust me?)

148
00:06:32,739 --> 00:06:34,218
Nange, do you still remember

149
00:06:34,219 --> 00:06:35,418
that princess dress you wanted

150
00:06:35,419 --> 00:06:37,098
back in elementary school?

151
00:06:37,099 --> 00:06:39,819
I had to go to three malls
before finally finding it for you.

152
00:06:39,820 --> 00:06:41,739
You've probably forgotten by now,
haven't you?

153
00:06:41,859 --> 00:06:43,020
Auntie,

154
00:06:43,700 --> 00:06:44,819
you just said

155
00:06:44,820 --> 00:06:46,499
that whenever Nange wanted something,

156
00:06:46,500 --> 00:06:48,098
you always found a way
to give it to her.

157
00:06:48,099 --> 00:06:50,338
I'll remember that.

158
00:06:50,339 --> 00:06:51,939
And what I can promise is,

159
00:06:51,940 --> 00:06:53,218
from this day forward,

160
00:06:53,219 --> 00:06:54,298
whatever Nange wants,

161
00:06:54,299 --> 00:06:56,659
whatever she deserves,
I can give it to her.

162
00:07:00,460 --> 00:07:02,178
Today, in front of our parents,

163
00:07:02,179 --> 00:07:04,418
I want to make three requests of Nange.

164
00:07:04,419 --> 00:07:05,418
First,

165
00:07:05,419 --> 00:07:06,459
stop locking yourself away

166
00:07:06,460 --> 00:07:07,778
inside the laboratory all the time.

167
00:07:07,779 --> 00:07:10,338
I know many talents and experts

168
00:07:10,339 --> 00:07:11,499
in the medical field.

169
00:07:11,620 --> 00:07:12,738
You should go out more,

170
00:07:12,739 --> 00:07:14,020
meet people, make friends.

171
00:07:14,060 --> 00:07:16,779
And those meaningless social circles?

172
00:07:16,780 --> 00:07:18,640
You don't have to force yourself
to deal with them.

173
00:07:18,687 --> 00:07:23,499
ظآزAll that I can
to just stand where I standظآز

174
00:07:23,500 --> 00:07:24,539
Second,

175
00:07:24,700 --> 00:07:26,220
treat yourself better.

176
00:07:27,260 --> 00:07:28,739
Whatever you want,

177
00:07:28,779 --> 00:07:31,179
whether it's clothes you want to buy,

178
00:07:31,219 --> 00:07:32,780
places you want to visit,

179
00:07:32,979 --> 00:07:34,259
or restaurants you want to try,

180
00:07:34,260 --> 00:07:35,940
you never need to look at the price tag.

181
00:07:36,139 --> 00:07:39,338
As long as you live comfortably and brightly,
your heart will naturally become brighter too.

182
00:07:39,339 --> 00:07:40,139
And,

183
00:07:40,140 --> 00:07:41,699
I'm willing to pay any price

184
00:07:41,700 --> 00:07:42,899
for your happiness.

185
00:07:42,900 --> 00:07:45,260
Because you deserve it.

186
00:07:46,979 --> 00:07:48,099
Third,

187
00:07:48,460 --> 00:07:50,899
whenever someone
or something makes you frown,

188
00:07:50,900 --> 00:07:52,098
don't carry it alone.

189
00:07:52,099 --> 00:07:53,220
Tell me.

190
00:07:53,299 --> 00:07:54,778
As your husband,

191
00:07:54,779 --> 00:07:56,538
it's my duty and responsibility

192
00:07:56,539 --> 00:07:58,659
to make sure the people who trouble you

193
00:08:00,380 --> 00:08:03,059
quietly disappear from your sight.

194
00:08:08,700 --> 00:08:11,140
I'm willing to protect this bond
of family for you.

195
00:08:13,460 --> 00:08:14,978
The dress fitting can wait.

196
00:08:14,979 --> 00:08:15,738
Come on.

197
00:08:15,739 --> 00:08:16,940
Let's eat first.

198
00:08:17,260 --> 00:08:18,419
Alright.

199
00:08:24,979 --> 00:08:26,179
Delicious.

200
00:08:34,860 --> 00:08:36,578
Let's stop just sitting here staring.

201
00:08:36,579 --> 00:08:37,820
Everyone dig in.

202
00:08:37,860 --> 00:08:38,818
Dear in-law,

203
00:08:38,819 --> 00:08:40,298
this is premium deep-sea fish maw.

204
00:08:40,299 --> 00:08:41,538
Great for beauty and skin care.

205
00:08:41,539 --> 00:08:42,779
Thank you.

206
00:08:43,659 --> 00:08:45,058
I made myself clear, right?

207
00:08:45,059 --> 00:08:47,060
From now on,
the Xu family and Huo family

208
00:08:47,100 --> 00:08:49,099
can maintain appearances publicly.

209
00:08:49,100 --> 00:08:50,139
But those two women,

210
00:08:50,140 --> 00:08:52,300
do not let them appear in front
of Nange again.

211
00:08:52,740 --> 00:08:54,259
Not even once.

212
00:08:55,059 --> 00:08:56,060
Understood?

213
00:08:56,100 --> 00:08:57,379
Understood.

214
00:09:06,579 --> 00:09:08,300
Thanks for tonight.

215
00:09:09,740 --> 00:09:10,820
It was nothing.

216
00:09:11,620 --> 00:09:13,139
You're pretty impressive, you know that?

217
00:09:13,140 --> 00:09:16,019
Li Wanru had barely started putting
on her fake act about dresses,

218
00:09:16,020 --> 00:09:16,979
and within five minutes,

219
00:09:16,980 --> 00:09:19,259
you already had Shen Yan
bring in all the props.

220
00:09:19,860 --> 00:09:22,460
More accurately,
three and a half minutes.

221
00:09:22,500 --> 00:09:23,820
How do you even do that?

222
00:09:23,860 --> 00:09:25,458
How I do it isn't important.

223
00:09:25,459 --> 00:09:29,580
I'm only responsible for making decisions
and fulfilling the promises I make to you.

224
00:09:29,620 --> 00:09:31,778
Being your special assistant
sounds exhausting.

225
00:09:31,779 --> 00:09:34,220
It's much better to be like me.
Being the wife is easier.

226
00:09:44,340 --> 00:09:45,580
I...

227
00:09:46,299 --> 00:09:47,219
I mean...

228
00:09:47,220 --> 00:09:49,259
you should give Shen Yan a raise.

229
00:09:51,100 --> 00:09:52,940
Don't worry. I already have it in mind.

230
00:09:53,459 --> 00:09:56,619
Actually, besides tonight's dinner,

231
00:09:56,620 --> 00:09:58,220
he also made progress on something else.

232
00:09:59,500 --> 00:10:01,859
He tracked down Dr. X's email.

233
00:10:02,140 --> 00:10:03,538
The network address

234
00:10:03,539 --> 00:10:05,538
had triple-layer encryption,

235
00:10:05,539 --> 00:10:06,499
but my tech department

236
00:10:06,500 --> 00:10:07,899
already broke through two layers.

237
00:10:07,900 --> 00:10:10,340
At the latest,
I'll have the final result tomorrow.

238
00:10:10,459 --> 00:10:11,418
(That fast?)

239
00:10:11,419 --> 00:10:13,060
(They already traced the IP address?)

240
00:10:13,779 --> 00:10:14,859
What's wrong?

241
00:10:16,900 --> 00:10:18,899
I-I just remembered

242
00:10:18,900 --> 00:10:20,938
I still haven't finished
revising my thesis.

243
00:10:20,939 --> 00:10:22,619
I'm heading back to work on it first.

244
00:10:42,779 --> 00:10:44,180
(Not here.)

245
00:10:58,620 --> 00:11:00,259
(Not here either.)

246
00:11:02,020 --> 00:11:03,379
(Where did they put)

247
00:11:03,380 --> 00:11:05,019
(that IP trace report?)

248
00:11:06,179 --> 00:11:08,499
(If I don't find it soon,
Huo Beiyan will be back any minute.)

249
00:11:08,500 --> 00:11:09,739
Mr. Huo.

250
00:11:17,419 --> 00:11:18,139
Mrs. Huo,

251
00:11:18,140 --> 00:11:20,300
these are the urgent files
Mr. Huo requested.

252
00:11:21,539 --> 00:11:22,820
Just leave them there.

253
00:11:23,220 --> 00:11:24,139
Understood.

254
00:11:26,219 --> 00:11:28,859
Why is this place such a mess?
I'll help him tidy up a little.

255
00:11:33,230 --> 00:11:35,120
(IP Trace Report)
(So it hasn't been delivered yet.)

256
00:11:35,740 --> 00:11:37,019
(There's still time.)

257
00:11:37,925 --> 00:11:39,495
(IP Trace Report)

258
00:11:48,187 --> 00:11:49,457
(IP Trace Report)

259
00:12:00,220 --> 00:12:01,580
Good afternoon, Mr. Huo.

260
00:12:11,500 --> 00:12:13,178
Tell the marketing director
to wait for me.

261
00:12:13,179 --> 00:12:14,499
I'll be there shortly.

262
00:12:16,659 --> 00:12:17,779
Hello.

263
00:12:17,819 --> 00:12:18,940
Wait.

264
00:12:21,020 --> 00:12:22,240
Why are you here?

265
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:24,000
Weren't you supposed
to be revising your thesis?

266
00:12:25,419 --> 00:12:26,859
Iظخ

267
00:12:27,900 --> 00:12:29,298
I wanted to come see you.

268
00:12:29,299 --> 00:12:30,460
Is that not allowed?

269
00:12:32,140 --> 00:12:34,299
Wait for me a second.
I just need to finish up some work.

